ctively.</td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 8px;line-height: 1.42857;vertical-align: top;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221)\">hide.bs.tab</td><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 8px;line-height: 1.42857;vertical-align: top;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221)\">This event fires when a new tab is to be shown (and thus the previous active tab is to be hidden). Use&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 13px;padding: 2px 4px;color: rgb(199, 37, 78);background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);border-radius: 4px\">event.target</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 13px;padding: 2px 4px;color: rgb(199, 37, 78);background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);border-radius: 4px\">event.relatedTarget</code>&nbsp;to target the current active tab and the new soon-to-be-active tab, respectively.</td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box\"><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 8px;line-height: 1.42857;vertical-align: top;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221)\">hidden.bs.tab</td><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 8px;line-height: 1.42857;vertical-align: top;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221)\">This event fires after a new tab is shown (and thus the previous active tab is hidden). Use&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 13px;padding: 2px 4px;color: rgb(199, 37, 78);background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);border-radius: 4px\">event.target</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-size: 13px;padding: 2px 4px;color: rgb(199, 37, 78);background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);border-radius: 4px\">event.relatedTarget</code>&nbsp;to ta